# Local static preview

The browsable static site for this project lives under **`local-repo/`** at the repo root (not the repo root itself).

When starting a local preview server (`python3 -m http.server`, `npx serve`, etc.), **`cd` into `local-repo/` first**, then bind/listen as usual.

Example:

```bash
cd local-repo && python3 -m http.server 5513
```

Then open `http://localhost:<port>/`.

The root URL **`/`** sends visitors to **`app.html`** (same idea as production **`/` → `/app`**). The SEA map landing page is **`home.html`**.
